Available now unfurnished 1 bedroom apartment in Old West
apartment_description:
Cozy well maintained, comfortable apartment near Amsterdam Center Very attractive monumental apartment of approximately 45 m2 in a prime location, in a quiet and pleasant street. Completely renovated a few years ago. Located on the edge of the center and yet quiet! Within walking distance of Kinkerstraat, Leidseplein, Jordaan and De Hallen. Pleasantly located on the 2nd floor with wide views on both sides. Living room is approximately 20 m² and has a cozy and luxurious open kitchen with all necessary equipment such as: a dishwasher, refrigerator with freezer, 4-burner gas stove, extractor hood, washing machine, dryer and microwave. Bedroom, shower The apartment has a spacious bedroom of approximately 10 m² with a small built-in wardrobe. Next to this bedroom is the bathroom which is equipped with a luxury shower with thermostat, sink and design radiator for your towels. Semi-upholstered You enter the hall through the communal upholstered staircase. The separate toilet, which is also accessible through the hall, is equipped with a fountain. The apartment is semi-furnished with a separate washing machine and dryer. The apartment has central heating.
Conditions:
- Rent is 1300,- excluding gas, water and light.
- Refundable deposit required equal to 2 months rent.
- Immediately available for longer than a year.
- Registration with the city hall is compulsory.

apartment_description:
This amazing city center apartment with two bedrooms and two bathrooms is located on a canal in the heart of the city center just next to the famous Leidseplein and Rijksmuseum!
This fully furnished 120 square meter apartment is located on the 2nd, 3rd floor and 4th floor of a monumental building, was completely renovated in 2012. It now features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a large open plan kitchen. The apartment is stylishly decorated with antiques and modern furniture and has 4 meter high celing!
When entering on the ground floor, you can reach the first floor by stairs where you find the entrance to the apartment. On the second floor the spacious dining room and open plan kitchen is located. The kitchen is equipped with dishwasher, oven, microwave and a Boretti 5 hob gas stove! All other kitchen supplies for daily use are provided as well. Adjacent to the kitchen you find the dining room with a dining table that seat 6. On the second floor you find the living room with comfortable sofa and two large sofa seats. The flat screen TV provided has over 100 international channels and wireless internet is provided. Adjacent to the living room you find the master bedroom with double bed and ensu9ite bathroom. The comfortable bathroom has a bath, vanity and toilet.
IN the spacious attic room with original beams you find 3 single beds and second bathroom. This bathroom has a shower, double wash basin and toilet.
Wooden flooring is used throughout the entire apartment.
Conditions:
- Minimum 1 year, longer possible.
- Rent is 2500,- exclusive utilities.
- Refundable deposit required.

Furnished 2 double bedrooms apartment between De Pijp and Oosterpark
apartment_description:
Light and sleek renovated and totally newly furnished 3-room apartment located on the second floor of the apartment complex 'Holland Veste' with balcony and a spacious private garden of approx. 40 m² in the private city garden.
Urban bustle at the front, a haven of peace at the rear! The special and beautifully landscaped garden is located on the southwest and is approx. 2000 m2!
The building "Holland Veste" was built in 1998 and therefore has all the comforts of a new apartment. The complex offers a high level of safety, comfort and privacy, thanks to the excellent insulation facilities and high-quality finish.
Lay-out:
Through the neat, shared entrance with elevator and staircase you will reach the second floor. On this floor you enter the central hall with access to all rooms. The living room with open kitchen is located at the front of the apartment with access to the hall and balcony which is facing East directly overlooking Wibautstraat.
The kitchen was renewed in 2016 and is equipped with Siemens appliances such as a built-in oven and dishwasher. The cooking island is equipped with electric cooker and a hood.
The two spacious bedrooms are both adjacent to the balcony. Centrally located is the modern bathroom which was renewed in 2017 and is equipped with a bath, shower, radiator and double sink with mirror with lighting.
Next to it is a separate room with connection for the washing machine. Separate toilet in the hall with a fountain and mirror with storage space. Furthermore, there is a floor of ceramic tiles with high plinths throughout the house.
At ground floor of the building you will find a spacious storage room, a communal bicycle storage and the private garden facing Southwest! This garden borders the common ecological courtyard.
Surroundings:
The apartment complex is located on the Wibautstraat, corner of the Amstel and near the Pijp.
The Wibautstraat is one of the bustling streets in Amsterdam East! Within walking distance are many hotspots such as the Volkshotel and (Club) Canvas, or "Loetje" Oost. In addition, you naturally find all the daily amenities such as an Albert Heijn, a pharmacy etc. The entrance to the Wibautstraat metro station is diagonally in front of the door and the accessibility of the A10 ring road per car is perfect (S112).
Details:
- Newly furnished completely in Oct 2018 with new furniture and electrical goods (eg. big refrigerator, washing machine, 55 inch 4k television)
- The kitchen is renewed in 2016
- Bathroom and toilet are renewed in 2017
- Private storage and balcony.
- Common bicycle storage
- Courtyard garden only for building residents (2000m²).
- Private garden of approx. 40 m²
- Rent is 1900,- exclusive utilities
- Refundable deposit required
- Minimum lease is 1 year, longer preferred
- Registration with the city hall is mandatory

Huge penthouse 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms terrace cellar garage
apartment_description:
Furnished or unfurnished as well. Corner penthouse of 161 m2 for rent and a storage space/wine cellar of 19 m2, all accessible by elevator, at the most beautiful spot of Amstelveen in apartment complex 'Le Jardin'. A unique opportunity for those who love luxury, quality and quietness in lush and green surroundings at the so called 'Gold coast'. Adjacent to parcs like the famous J.P. Thijssepark and the Broersepark and in the direct vicinity of the Amsterdam Forrest. The penthouse was designed by architect Nanne Schuiveling and is equipped with all necessary luxury and executed in high-grade materials from leading brands. All build-in closets were specially made by well-known furniture maker Marcel Klusters.
Via the central lobby one reaches the penthouse on the second floor. The whole apartment has beautifully brush-painted doors and on the floor throughout the apartment Mosa floor tiles. The entire apartment has heated floors which can be regulated for each room individually. The hall with separate restroom and closet leads to the spacious and bright living room of 68m². The living is surrounded by a terrace and all 13 so called door windows of the apartment are equipped with automatic sunscreens. On the outside of the penthouse there are four large remote-controlled sunscreens a well. Further the whole apartment has hotel-grade climate control and there's an open fire place (gas) for extra ambience and comfort.
The spacious dining room on the side of the apartment has a view on the green and lush surroundings and is ideal for a nice dinner with friends and family. The half-open kitchen from leading brand Bulthaupt looks like new and is fully fitted with built-in appliances and has a high-grade gas stove with six pits and two ovens (SMEG). From the living room there is a corridor that leads you to the 3 bedrooms, two bathrooms and spacious laundry room. The master bedroom at the back of the apartment has a walk-in closet and offers a fantastic view at the green courtyard. From the master bedroom we enter the luxurious bathroom with Italian mosaics, king-size Jacuzzi, and taps by Dornbracht. There is a hydrophore pump for extra water pressure and a soft water installation.
The other three bedrooms are located on the front side of the apartment of which the largest is 30m² and has a build-in closet and large doors opening to the terrace. Furthermore there's the second nice bathroom with shower and sink.
The large terrace around the penthouse is 60m² and has a separate dining and sun-deck. The terrace is equipped with LED-lighting that switches on and off automatically at sunset and on timer. The apartment has a high-grade security alarm that can be switched on and off remotely by mobile from every possible location. Very large separate storage of 19 m² in the basement of the building. Optional there are 1 or 2 spacious parking spaces available for sale.
Besides the lush and green surroundings, parks and the forest, the apartment complex 'The Jardins' top-location has easy access to main highways like A2, A4, A9 and beltway A10 and also main airport Amsterdam Schiphol, Business Center Zuidas, the beautiful and fashionable shopping center of Amstelveen and the charming Old Village (Oude Dorp). The International School and other elementary and secondary schools can be found in the vicinity.
Conditions:
- Immediately available.
- Minimum lease is 1 year, longer possible.
- Rent is 4000,- exclusive utilities and service costs.
- Two months refundable deposit required.
Specifications:
- Floor area ca. 161 m² (NEN-2580 standards),
- Built in 2006,
- Optional there are 1 or 2 parking lots for sale,
- Separate storage unit in the substructure,
- Electrically operated screens throughout the whole apartment,
- Video-intercom system,
- Alarm system,
- Active association of homeowners "Le Jardin", administration is outsourced to Starrip VvE Beheer,
- Service charges ca. € 336,-- per month

This 3 Bedroom unfurnished Apartment of 79m2 with a deep balcony overlooking the courtyard on the 2nd floor of a well-maintained complex is now available.

1600 ALL INCLUSIVE! Spacious studio with garden and garage
apartment_description:
Well-kept studio apartment (furnished) of approx. 40 m² with private garden and a fantastic view over
the canals. The property is situated on the Ertskade on the Sporenburg
peninsula The property is located on the water of the Ertshaven in the Eastern Docklands, All
conceivable facilities are within reach. You can cycle to, for example, the Central Station or the City
Center within 8 minutes, while the IJ tram takes less than 5 minutes. With tram line 7 you are also
within 10 minutes in the heart of the city but there is also a direct connection to Amsterdam-Noord with
the ferry. The Brazil shopping center and many entertainment venues (Club Panama, Lloyd Hotel, The
Harbor Club) are within walking distance. Within a few minutes you are by car via the Piet Hein tunnel
on the A10 ring road. Layout: Ground floor: Private entrance from the street. It concerns a space of
approximately 40 m² with a kitchen and bathroom, so that two spaces are created without the use of
partitions. The walls are smoothly finished. The kitchen is equipped with a large refrigerator, electric
hob, hot air oven and a built-in dishwasher. The bathroom has a toilet, sink with chest of drawers and
shower. A tumble dryer is available in a small closed space. The studio has a loft bed (bed 1.40 cm x
2.00), corner sofa bed, large wardrobe, dining table with bench and chairs, extra sofa bed a large
cupboard for books, etc. and there are beautiful curtains. And ........ a private garden of 4 by 4 square
meters!
Conditions:
- Rent is 1600,- per month including service costs, electricity, heat and water. The space
is only suitable / intended for a single person or a couple.
- Deposit / bank guarantee is 3,000 euros
- Rental is through a temporary contract of up to 2 years
- Smoking and / or pets are not allowed in the rented property
- Registration with the city hall is compulsory.

Sharing ok 3 bedrooms apartment near Bijlmer station
apartment_description:
- Lift available!
- Sharing by 3 friends is allowed!
- No agency fee nor hidden costs!
A fully furnished 2 double and 1 single bedroom apartment of 80m2 with a nice balcony of 4m2.
This very nice light and spacious 4 rooms apartment of 80m2 is situated at a great location in Amsterdam Zuidoost just around the corner of the Arena railway-, metro- and busstation and shopping center Amsterdamse Poort.
Many international companies from the business and financial services like ING, ABN, Graydon, Deutsche Bank, Telfort and Cisco are located in this area.
It can be shared with 3 people. And all 3 people can of course register with the municipality.
The apartment has 2 large bedrooms with double beds and a singles bedroom. The singles bedroom can house furniture for a baby or a full size (single) bed.
The spacious kitchen is well equipped with a large fridge, gas stove and many miscellaneous kitchen appliances. (no dishwasher). All the furniture is in a very good, almost new, condition.
The apartment is located on the 4th floor and comes with a storagebox.
- Rent: 2000,- exclusive utilities.
- Deposit: 2500,- and refundable.
- Possible to register with the city hall.

apartment_name: Furnished 1 bedroom apartment with sea views
apartment_description:
Perfect for a couple or a single.
A fully (and newly) furnished 1 bedroom 60m2 apartment in a fantastically reformed old grainary.
A lift will bring you to the apartment on the 3th floor. Its location is perfect for every boat-loving individual, giving you clear views over ‘het IJ’. The apartment is close to city centre and only 1,5km from Central Station and offers stunning views of sun risings and sun sets from the apartment.
Entrée, separate toilet, bathroom with shower and bath tub, washing machine. Open kitchen with micro-oven, living room with views on ‘het IJ’. Separate, large, bedroom with views on the ‘oude Houthaven’ and lots of storage facilities.
Optional: parking space, 195 per month in underground parking system
- Rent: 1475,- excl utilities
- Deposit: 2500
- Minimum lease is 12 month, longer is preferred.
- For at least 1 year, longer possible.
- Registration with the city hall is compulsory

apartment_name: Unfurnished 4 bedrooms house with garden parking terrace and patio
apartment_description:
Experience the pleasant living space of this bright unfurnished corner house of approximately 208 m² with spacious living room, conservatory, three bedrooms, bathroom with separate bath and shower, large south-facing garden, side garden on the water on the west and a large basement with another possibility for fourth bedroom. Located in one of the best family locations in Amsterdam.
This particularly attractive family home has a beautifully landscaped south-facing rear garden, with a back entrance, which is securely protected by a fence. The garden gives a lot of privacy and plenty of room for your children to play. The house is in a child-friendly environment on a quiet street with all amenities in close proximity.
Coming home to this spacious family home is coming home to an excellent house with a warm ambiance. There is easy parking right in front of the house and a spacious, private place for bike parking.
The Amsterdamse Bos, Gelderlandplein, Supermarkets, Zuidas, VU University Amsterdam, VU medical center, both International and Dutch primary and secondary schools, various sports clubs, medical facilities, public transport links and roadways are all within easy access.
LAYOUT
Entrance to spacious hall with recessed spotlights, wardrobe, guest toilet and stairs to the first-floor and basement. To the right the spacious living room with conservatory, sliding doors to garden, working fireplace, recessed spotlights, tiled floor and underfloor heating. Kitchen with appliances such as gas hob, dishwasher, oven and refrigerator with 3-drawer freezer. Access to the side garden by the kitchen door.
On the first-floor landing, a very spacious Master bedroom with sliding doors to the south-facing balcony, beech wood floors, wardrobes and a view of the beautiful garden. Opposite two more spacious bedrooms also with wardrobes, tilt-and-turn windows and wood flooring. The bathroom has a skylight, a bathtub, a bathroom cabinet with double sink, a separate walk-in shower and a toilet. The bathroom is tiled to the ceiling.
The spacious basement (rare for Amsterdam) includes a hall/storage area, laundry room with washing machine and separate dryer and the central heating system. Additionally, there is a spacious extra carpeted room with wardrobes which can be used as a studio/office or fourth/guest bedroom.
PARTICULARITIES
- The rental price is 3750,- per month including curtains, wardrobes, washer/dryer etc.
- The rental price excludes gas, water, electricity and internet.
- Contract cost is 300,- inclusive vat.
Some distances to sum it up:
-6 min cycle to the Zuidas
-6 min cycle to Amsterdam International Community School (AICS main campus)
-11 min cycling to British School of Amsterdam
-19 min cycle to International School of Amsterdam (Amstelveen)
-24 min cycling to the Dam
-8 min cycling to Oud-Zuid
-14 min cycling to the Pipe
-14 min by taxi/car to Schiphol
-400 m to tram/metro stop A. J. Ernststraat
-500 m to bus/tram stop VU
-15 min walk to South Station (from there North-South line to center or Amsterdam North
DETAILS
-large family home of about 208 m2
-3 bedrooms
-basement with 4th bedroom
-large South facing garden
-closed by fence with entrance from the street
-side Garden facing West overlooking water
-quiet child-friendly neighborhood
-easy parking in front
-all facilities within walking distance
-lot's of recreation nearby
-insulation glass through the whole house
-floor heating on the ground floor
-fireplace
-electronically controlled shutters
-electronic blinds with sensor operation master bedroom
-garden maintenance service available

No agency fee required nor hidden costs for the tenant.
Available per today!
A furnished 2 bedrooms bright and practical apartment (approx.81 m2) , with a sunny balcony on the southwest and a storage room in the basement. Fully equipped with a laminate floor, neatly finished walls and a kitchen with built-in appliances.
The bright and spacious living room, like the open kitchen, is finished with a laminate floor. The spacious balcony can be reached by sliding doors. The balcony is conveniently located on the southwest. The kitchen is located on the left side of the living room. It is a modern kitchen with the following equipment; 4-burner gas stove with oven function, extractor hood, oven and a dishwasher. The presence of a utility room is striking, with a surprising amount of storage space.
The apartment is located on the 2nd floor of a well-maintained complex from 2003. Around the corner from Pieter Calandlaan and within cycling distance of Osdorpplein (3 min), Sloterplas (5 min), Station Lelylaan (9 min), Hoofddorpplein (14 min ) and the Nieuwe Meer (15 min). Osdorp is valued as a socially safe, green and child-friendly neighborhood. This attractive apartment is centrally located to shopping facilities (Pieter Calandlaan, Osdorpplein), public transport (Tram 1), roads and recreational opportunities.

apartment_description:
Fully Furnished 3 story family house of approx 100m2. Ideal for a small family or a couple.
Located in a very central and popular residential location, well maintained house with attached stone shed. Front garden and nice landscaped, privacy-offering backyard with deck located on a water feature. The garden will be serviced before check-in of a new tenant.
The house is well maintained and equipped with a good size kitchen, neat bathroom and has 2 bedrooms and a spacious attic floor where a 3rd bedroom has been realized. Ample parking space in the immediate vicinity.
The location is excellent, close to all conceivable amenities such as the shopping center, various schools, nurseries as well as the Haarlemmermeerse forest and the Toolenburger lake. The Toolenburg bus stop with direct bus connections to Schiphol, Haarlem, Amsterdam and the Hoofddorp railway station is also within walking distance.
Layout: entrance, hall with meter cupboard and toilet with sink, bright living room with stairs cupboard and access to the secluded backyard, semi-open kitchen with all kinds of built-in appliances (including oven, dishwasher, fridge / freezer, ceramic hob and extractor). The living area of ??the living room and kitchen together is ± 38 m².
1st floor: Landing, spacious rear bedroom (± 15 m²) with Velux roof windows, bathroom with shower cabin, toilet and sink, front bedroom (± 11 m²).
2nd floor: Attic / bedroom / hobby room (± 6 m²) with central heating boiler and Velux roof window.
Particularities:
- NO smoking inside the house.
- Beloved and centrally located residential location
- Backyard offering privacy and situated on the water with wooden platform
- Ample parking space in the immediate vicinity
- 3 bedrooms
- Rent: 1750,- excluding all bills
- Reundable deposit: 2500,-.
- Minimum lease is 1 year, longer preferred.
- Registration with the city hall is mandatory.

Ground floor duplex house 4 bedrooms 2 bathrooms garden
apartment_description:
Specifics:
• 3500,- (ex bills) per month
• Available for 12 or 24 months
• Parking permit possible within 1-2 months.
This unique Amsterdam historic 170 m2 double floor townhouse is renovated with charming original historic elements preserved. And lies just outside Amsterdam’s busy city center in a hip and picturesque, residential neighborhood in Amsterdam West (Baarsjes).The house offers 170 m2 square living space, is fully furnished, “turn-key ready” and features two floors offering a large living area, kitchen, 3-4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 toilets.Direct access to public transport (trams 13 and 19, busline 15 and 18). Close to motorways and parking permit available.
Available fully furnished with all new furniture, brand new washing- and drying machines and new 50” UHD 4K TV.
Noteworthy places you can cycle to within 15 minutes:
• Amsterdam Dam (10 min)
• Amsterdam Centraal Station (12 min)
• WTC/Zuidas Amsterdam (15 min)
• Westerpark (10 min)
• FoodHallen (3 min)
• Amsterdam Sloterdijk (12 min)

Now available furnished 2 bedrooms apartment nearby Rembrandtpark
apartment_description:
For at least 1 year, longer possible, apartment for rent on Postjeskade (Baarsjes): situated on the second floor, 2 bedrooms, a living room, 1 bathroom with shower and toilet, a kitchen and a balcony.
The apartment is fully furnished, light and located on the channel. The second bedroom has a foldable couch which can become a double bed and therefore the apartment is suitable for sharing by two.
- Rental price is 1650 p/m excl. utilities.
- One month refundable deposit required.
- Registration with the city hall is compulsory.
Tram lines 1 and 17 and bus line 15, Rembrandtpark, Vondelpark, Erasmuspark, Surinameplein, Overtook, Lelylaan station, shops, supermarkets Aldi and Albert Heijn, a pharmacy, dental and general practices are nearby. 10-15 minutes by bike to the center.

Furnished 2 bedrooms apartment near Rembrandtpark and Vondelpark
apartment_description:
Fully furnished renovated apartment in De Baarsjes nearby the Overtoom, Rembrandtpark and Vondelpark. It consists of a sunny living room, fully equipped kitchen, washer and dryer, bathroom, separate toilet, nice balcony and 2 well sized bedrooms. Possible to get a parking permit from the City Hall!
Conditions:
- Minimum lease is 1 year, longer possible.
- Rent is 2000,- exclusive g/w/e/ and internet.
- Two months refundable deposit required.

apartment_name: Available furnished 2 bedrooms apartment with garage
apartment_description:
Minimum lease is 1 year, longer preferred.
A modern fully furnished 2 bedroom apartment on the 1st floor. Measuring approximately 75m2, it offers a great living experience for a small family or couple.
The apartment was build in 2008 and has a natural-wood floor throughout the whole apartment. The kitchen is equiped with all amenities. There are 2 bedrooms in typical set-up. A large master and a smaller bedroom for a guest/child or to be converted into a study/office
With the apartment comes a private parking spot. Visitors can enjoy free parking on the street. There is also a good sized storage box to put away all your suitcases etc.
Located in Abcoude within 1km from the Golfclub Hoge-Dijk. The location in relation to cities like Amsterdam and Utrecht can not be better, you can reach them quickly and easily by car or by public transport! The train station is a 1 minute walk. Walking / biking distance to AMC Hospital and Gein in Amsterdam Zuidoost
The cozy village of Abcoude is within walking distance. The village is equipped with all “conveniences” such as bakery, butcher, (clothing) shops, restaurants.
- Rent: 1650,- excl utilities
- Deposit: 2500,-
- Registration with the city hall is compulsory.

apartment_name: Brand new furnished 1 bedroom apartment near Centraal sation
apartment_description:
Newly built apartment looking for its first inhabitant! Beautiful, very bright apartment just 10 minutes away from the Central Station. All furniture and utilities are BRAND NEW. This apartment is located in the Houthavens area, a newly constructed neighborhood in old Dutch style. Perfect for 1 or 2 persons that want a luxurious and comfortable stay while working in Amsterdam for a year or two.
The apartment consists of a big living room with 2 huge windows on the 4th floor of the building. You will have a balcony to enjoy the weather, although there are 2 big parks nearby. The whole apartment is heated by floor heating and climate control. The bedroom contains a large king-size bed for 2 persons. There is a big closet for your clothes and the curtains make sure to block light so you can have a good sleep. The kitchen contains a Samsung microwave and oven, Nespresso machine, fridge and dishwasher. There is also a washing machine to wash your clothes. The apartment is located in a newly constructed building and neighborhood. All apartments are isolated with modern standards against noise pollution.
Located on the IJ, De Houthaven offers so much; numerous creative companies have established themselves in the area as well as schools, trendy bars and restaurants such as Karaat. The property is easily accessible by buses 22, 48 and 281. The central station can be reached in 10 minutes by bike. The A10 ring road can be reached via the s101 and s102. De Houthavens are climate neutral, car-free and very popular due to the spacious layout. It is only a few minutes from both Jordaan and Westerpark and perhaps 10 minutes from Vondelpark, Old West, Leidseplein and the old center.
Conditions:
- Immediately available.
- Minimum lease is 12 months.
- Rent is 1700,- exclusive g/w/e and internet.
- Refundable deposit required.
- Registration with the city hall is mandatory!
- Underneath parking spot is optional and costs a bit more.

apartment_name: Huge canal apartment 3 bedroom plus fireplace lift parking canal view
apartment_description:
Located on the most beautiful spot of the Keizersgracht near the Reguliersgracht and Utrechtstestraat we offer you this cozy apartment with a living area of ​​approx. 118m² plus a large storage room. This property includes a lovely bright living room with open kitchen, 3 spacious bedrooms, a luxurious bathroom and is located on the 2nd floor of the well maintained canal house.
Location:
This particular canal house "De Factorij" is situated in a prime location in the historic city center of Amsterdam, on one of the most beautiful places of the Keizersgracht, between the Vijzelstraat and the Reguliersgracht in. Very centrally located with, among others, the Stopera, Royal Theater Carré and Museum de Hermitage. In the vicinity there is a wide range of international museums, excellent restaurants and cozy lunchrooms. The car can be found in the parking garage under the Stopera and public transport. Both the Central Station and Amstel Station are nearby. Around June 2018 the North - South metro line will be opened, one stop of which is within walking distance.
Layout:
Ground floor:
Spacious entrance of three monumental canal houses with elevator and one common staircase.
Second floor:
Spacious hall that gives access to all rooms. Separate toilet. Guest bathroom with walk-in shower and sink. At the front is the cozy bright living room with fireplace and open kitchen. This kitchen is equipped with various appliances such as refrigerator, 5-burner gas stove, steam oven, oven, microwave and a dishwasher. From the living room you have a beautiful view over the Keizersgracht. Currently, the apartment has three bedrooms, one of which is in use as a walk-in closet, and here are the connections for the washer and dryer.
A work / study space has been created on the landing. In the back house are two spacious bedrooms and adjoining the rear bedroom you will find the bathroom with walk-in shower, sink and toilet. The rear bedroom also gives a nice view over the well-known gardens between the Keizersgracht and Herengracht.
Keizersgracht:
To Emperor Maximliaan, archduke of Austria, who in 1489 gave Amsterdam the privilege to wear the imperial crown on the coat of arms.
(Source: City Atlas Amsterdam)
Particularities
- Rent is 4000,- exclusive utilities
- Elevator present
- National monument
- Storage on the ground floor
- Wooden floor
- Monthly service costs 350, -
- Active and healthy VvE, professionally managed by Velzel VvE management
- Delivery in consultation,
- Parking via permit system (Municipality of Amsterdam)

Good for sharing furnished 2 double bedrooms apartment near WTC
apartment_description:
Modern spacious furnished apartment of approximately 108m² on the 6th floor in a very nice, quiet and green area called Buitenveldert. The apartment, located on the 6th floor, can be reached by elevators or stairs.
Layout:
Entrance/hall, spacious hallway with intercom/videophone, utility closet with electricity meter, 2 bedrooms, toilet with sink, modern kitchen with some built-in appliances. A closet for wash machine and dryer. Nice and modern bathroom with a bath tub, separate shower and sink. Very nice bright and spacious living room with dining area and access to the balcony (south facing). Separate storage on the ground floor of the building.
Location:
The area has a spacious set up. The apartment is surrounded by beautiful parks and is centrally situated close to (international) schools and the VU university as well as the south axis and station South/WTC.
The area features numerous amenities that will make life comfortable such as convenient shops nearby (supermarkets Albert Heijn XL & Jumbo), as well as a state of the art shopping mall called Gelderlandplein. Excellent access to public transport (tram 5 and hi-speed tram 51, busses and trams 4, 16 and 24 to the city center). Station Zuid/WTC is also close by with a train to Schiphol airport (1 stop, 6 minutes). Easy access to the motorways A-4, A-9 and A-10. Within a 10-minute walk you will find yourself in the Amsterdam Forest. Buitenveldert is also well known for its sports accommodations.
Conditions:
- rent is 2100,- exclusive utilities
- refundable deposit required
Features:
- centrally located
- the apartment has double glazing,
- parking by license, directly available
- easy parking
- balcony facing south
- storage
- sharing posible

apartment_name: Unfurnished duplex house 2 bedrooms 2 bathrooms garden garage terrace
apartment_description:
IT WILL BE DELIVERED UNFURNISHED ONLY!
Located on the Eastern Docklands.
Unfurnished and vacant as of today for at least 1 year, longer prefreed. A gorgeous multipurpose house of 140 m2 with parking place (carport), storage room and a roof terrace (approx 16 m2) on the South. The property has a beautiful location on the Sporenburg peninsula, in the former Ertshaven. Behind the house is the large garden of about 35 m2, unique inside Amsterdam city ring. The house was built in 1996 and designed by the famous office Neutelings Riedijk Architects. Ground Floor: Through the lockable carport you will access the house and the laundry room with washing machine and dryer connection. From the hall, with stairs to the 1st Floor, access to the rear bedroom / garden room and luxury bathroom with shower, double sink, toilet, bidet and towel radiator. The ground floor has a ceiling height of 3.25 meters, bedroom / garden room with access to the well maintained garden of approx 35 m2. Spread over three levels with a height of 1.50 meters. Garden consists of a hardwood deck, plant boxes and a gravel surface. 1st Floor: The spacious bedroom is equipped with a private Bathroom including toilet, a sink and a shower. 2nd Floor: The living area is 80 m2 with a roof terrace of 16 m2 (situated at the South). The large open kitchen floor is extremely light and pleasant. The floor is divided into several areas, the living room is located at the front and has a view on the water.
Neighbourhood: The Eastern Docklands is a unique residential neighbourhood surrounded by water. Excellent infrastructure and close to the city center. Public transport nearby, in about 5 minutes with tram 26 or 10 you will be at central station or the center.
- Monthly rent is 2200,- .
- Refundable deposit is 2 months.
- Registration with the city hall is possible.

Luxury spacious canal house 4 bedrooms garden garage and dock
apartment_description:
Located at IJburg district.
Lovely, spacious and light canal house. The house is approximately 145m² with a nice backyard with afternoon and evening sun, two parking spaces on private courtyard and a mooring for the boat at the front. The house has three floors and counts no less than 4 bedrooms, expandable to 5 bedrooms. The house is located on the canal, a lovely place with morning sun at the front and a mooring for the boat in front of the door.
Surroundings:
With close to all nice restaurants, the harbor of IJburg and shops for daily shopping, including a delicious bakery, the Dane and of course the shopping center. With various recreation parks in the neighborhood such as, football field at the door, Theo van Gogh park, the Diemerpark and Blijburg. Excellent roads to the A1, the A10 and by tram within 15 minutes on Amsterdam CS.
IJburg offers enough space to live, to recreate and above all to enjoy the outdoors at a stone's throw from the city center of Amsterdam!
A child-friendly neighborhood with several good schools and BSOs within walking distance and a house with a common private area as an extra playground and wonderful on the water.
Ground floor
Entrance, a hall with access to all rooms. Lovely open entrance, extra workspace, a toilet and a spacious stairs cupboard. Large windows, the front and a high ceiling of 3.30 make the house extra light. From the garden you can reach the two parking spaces, the bicycle shed and the private court. At the front of the house a terrace with morning sun an almost unused road and a mooring for the boat.
First floor
Workroom / meeting room / master bedroom with adjacent bathroom with bath, shower, double sink and toilet. There is also the possibility for an additional workplace here.
Second floor
Spacious landing, 2 children's rooms and 1 spacious master bedroom or possibility to split into 2 bedrooms, storage room with washing machine, a separate toilet. Storage space is prepared for possible conversion to extra bathroom.
Technology. This house is ready for the future with glass fiber, and internet cables to the 1st and 2nd floor for optimal multimedia use.

- Minimum lease is a year, preferably longer.
- Rent is 2750,- exclusive utilities
- Refundable deposit required.

apartment_description:
New and located right in the Centre of 'Stadshart' Amstelveen on the 2nd floor is this beautiful completely renovated furnished two-bedroom apartment of app 110m² with a spacious living room with open plan kitchen with kitchen unit, a sunny terrace facing South and a modern bathroom with large walk-in shower, a bathtub and a extra large sink.
This apartment has a spacious hall, separate toilet, a utility room where the washing machine and dryer are located and there is a private storage room in the basement of the building, where you can also find the communal bike shed. Through the whole apartment lays a superior quality laminate floor.
Layout:
Ground floor: entrance, with doorbells-and mailbox tableau and staircase or elevator.
Second floor: entrance to the apartment through the corridor with meter cupboard. Hall which provides access to all rooms with videophone installation. Two bedrooms (12 m 2 and 13 m 2) located on the quiet back of the complex. Modern, spacious bathroom with washbasin with mirror, bathtub and walk-in shower. Spacious separate toilet with toilet and fountain. Spacious living room with large windows over the entire width of the apartment. Through a sliding door access to the terrace located on the South and open view. New white kitchen with kitchen island and all necessary appliances. Storage/ utility room with fridge, washing machine, dryer and heating system. In addition, the apartment has an external storage room (6m²) situated in the basement.
Location:
In city center of Amstelveen with all facilities including the theatre, the famous Cobra Museum, library, stores like Bijenkorf, Zara, H & M, etc. and various restaurants and cafés are within walking distance as well as the bus station Amstelveen (with bus 300 are you within fifteen minutes on Schiphol Plaza) and tram line 5 to Amsterdam Central Station. The property is also easily accessible by car (A2, A9 and A10) and parking is available in the parking garage located under the town square or through a parking permit to the ' Gallery '.

Quoted rental price is 2000,- exclusive of utilities (gas, water, electricity, tv and internet)

Luxuous canal house with 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms terrace garden garage
apartment_description:
Photos upon request!
Ths spacious 3 storey house designed by an architect with a view across the docklands in the hip and popular Ijburg neighbourhood of Amsterdam.
This attractive property comprises a generous 177 m2 of living space plus a further 33 m2 with the two indoor garages.
Ground floor:
Entrance can be via one of the two electronically controlled garage doors. There is then an entrance hall with meter cupboard, cloakroom facilities, and separate WC with wash basin.
On the garden side of the property is a spacious area which could be used as a home office or alternatively as an extra bedroom. On this level is also a second, custom-made design kitchen, ideal for entertaining guests, particularly as it adjoins the garden. This garden has been lovingly landscaped with plenty of greenery and ornate wooden elements. The view over the bay as well as the southwest position adds real value to your lifestyle in our beautiful and historic city.
First floor:
Generous living room with access to a spacious terrace at the rear. The open kitchen with cooking island is of course fully equipped and implemented with all high quality appliances and materials including a worktop of Belgian blue stone. Extra atmosphere is created by a wood-fired fireplace with attractive glass panelling.
Second floor:
Landing with access to 3 bedrooms and two bathrooms. The very large master bedroom is located at the rear of the property and has a large floor-to-ceiling window, allowing maximum enjoyment of the view.
There are 2 bedrooms at the front.
The luxurious bathroom has natural light through two skylights and is equipped with a spacious bathtub, rain shower and a wash basin.
The second bathroom has a walk-in shower and wash basin, while on this level is also a separate WC.
Third floor:
A fixed staircase to the roof structure gives access to a roof terrace on the other side, ideal for relaxation.
From sun orientation to choice of materials, really everything in this house is well thought through!
The whole of this property has been lovingly and from to toe designed to combine the best of style and comfort, with underfloor heating and pump heating system to save you on your energy bills.
Location: Ijburg
The shopping center IJburg and the cosy harbour are both within cycling distance. Around the corner are schools, shops and high quality restaurants. The centre of the historic city of Amsterdam is at your fingertips via the very convenient tram 26 will takes you right to Central Station within 15 minutes.
Conditions:
Quoted rental price is 3800,- exclusive of utilities (gas, water, electricity, tv and internet).
Minimum lease is a year, longer preferred.

Semi furnished 2 bedrooms apartment with lift and garage
apartment_description:
SEMI FURNISHED 2 bedrooms apartment located in Amsterdam Southeast near metro station Gaasperplas which is served by line 53. It features a huge sunny living room overlooking the greenery, huge balcony, separate toilet, fully equipped open kitchen, bathroom with sink, shower and bath, storage room, 1 master bedroom and a smaller one. The building has 2 lift and the indoor garage is included in the rental price.
Conditions:
- Minimum lease is 12 months, longer preferred.
- Immediately available.
- Sharing is allowed by 2 non family individuals or a officially married couple and a friend.
- Rent is 1600,- exclusive g/w/e/internet and city taxes.
- Refundable deposit required.
- Registration with the city hall is mandatory.
- Proof of income and work contract is mandatory.

apartment_name: Furnished 2 bedrooms modern apartment near Arena Stadium
apartment_description:
Rent is 1700,- exclusive utilities.
Refundable deposit required
Registration with the city hall is mandatory
This furnished 2 bedroom apartment of approx 80m2.
Perfect for a couple and a single
The modern apartment is located in a very green and car-free environment, on the first floor of a small complex that was completed in 2011. The apartment is fully insulated, gas-free, has underfloor heating and a north-facing balcony with unobstructed views over the park!
Both bedrooms (one double and one single) are equipped with new beds and bedding.
The apartment is very central to various facilities. In the complex you will find primary school Het Klaverblad and there are secondary schools in the immediate vicinity. For a long walk you can go to the Bijlmerpark or the Bijlmerweide and the Gaasperplas is within cycling distance.
For daily shopping or a day of shopping you can go to the Amsterdamse Poort shopping center. You can also enjoy a night out, both the Ziggo Dome, AFAS Live, the Pathé Arena and the Amsterdam ArenA are within cycling distance and only a few hundred meters away you will find the indoor food halls ‘World of Food’.
Public transport including buses 41, 44 and 285 and metro stations Strandvliet (700m), Venserpolder (800m), Amsterdam Bijlmer Arena (1.2km) and Duivendrecht (1.3km) are within walking distance. From Amsterdam Bijlmer Arena railway station you are at Amsterdam Central Station with 10 minutes and from Duivendrecht station there is a direct train connection with Schiphol. Finally, you are within 5 minutes by car on the ring A10 or on the A9

apartment_name: Furnished renovated duplex nearby Jordaan with 2 double bedrooms
apartment_description:
Completely renovated 3 rooms-apartment in an old warehouse (monument). Situated on Prinseneiland (an Island) on walking distance from Central Station, Westerpark and the Jordaan. The apartment is very nicely furnished and well equipped. There are wooden floors throughout the whole apartment.
Rent is 2100,- exclusive utilities which cost around 150,- monthly.
Refundable deposit required.
Minimum lease is a year, longer preferred.
GROUND FLOOR:
Private storage room of 6m2.
FIFTH FLOOR:
Entrance. Toilet. Big living room with open kitchen, dining area and sitting area with open fire place.
SIXTH FLOOR:
Bathroom with spacious bath, separate shower, washing machine/dryer and sink. Separate toilet and storage. Big bedroom of 21m2. Spacious second (bed)room with working place.

Cozy 1 bedroom fully furnished apartment near the Jordaan
apartment_description:
Well located this cozy 2 rooms apartment – 50m2 in Amsterdam Westerpark.
This attractive apartment with balcony is located on the edge of the Westerpark and near the city center of Amsterdam. This property is totally report. A fully equipped kitchen, a dining table with chairs, sofa, washing machine + dryer, vacuum cleaner etc .
Notice period: 1 month per the first of the next month
Price: 1600 excl.
Registration: Yes (one person preferred)
Reaction: per mail
Deposit: 2 months rent and refundable
Layout
The living room (20 m2) has its own access to the balcony and access to the modern kitchen (8 m2). The kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher, fridge, freezer and a cooker (gas) with extractor. Through the hall you reach a bedroom (20m2) equipped with a bathroom.
Extras:
TV, fast internet, sonos, all surround system and automatic lighting via app
Possibility to rent extra storage space in the attic.
